S.FORM: Puerto rico hya' ga cyux maki' tay 18 15 N, 66 30 W na cung-Meco syuw. kwara' kinghciyan niya' 13,791 sq km (maki' tay 163ginkgan kin wahci') (kinwhci' niya' ga 8,870 sq km , kinwhci' na lawsayan wsilung hya' ga 4,921 sq km) Kinkhmayan kwara' squliq hya' ga 3,578,056. Pinbcyan naha' sni' naha' rhzyal hya' iy pqmahun hya' ga 22% , lhlahuy hya' ga 63.20%, sni' naha' sa pptzyuwaw sa bzinah hya' ga 14.80%. spzyang qalang na Kokka' spzyang naha' krahu' qalang hya' ga San Juan. snyan kinramat inlungan na Kokka' snyan kinramat inlungan na Kokka' hya' ga 4 na tay mpitu' byacing na qutux kawas. mrhuw Kokka' mrhuw Kokka' ta' misuw hya' ga Donald John Trump, aring ryax 20 squ byacing tay 1 sa kawas 2017 lga, musa' spazyang balay ms'rux kya la. cinkhulan sa knita' sa brbiru' CIA 外交部
